## Best Practices

### Do

```typescript
// Use select for specific fields (reduces data transfer)
const users = await prisma.user.findMany({
  select: { id: true, name: true },
});

// Use transactions for related operations
await prisma.$transaction(async (tx) => {
  // Multiple related operations
});

// Index frequently queried fields
// In schema: @@index([email, createdAt])

// Use pagination
const users = await prisma.user.findMany({
  take: 20,
  skip: page * 20,
  cursor: lastId ? { id: lastId } : undefined,
});
```

### Don't

```typescript
// Don't fetch all relations by default
const users = await prisma.user.findMany({
  include: { posts: true, profile: true }, // Only when needed
});

// Don't use raw queries unless necessary
const users = await prisma.$queryRaw`SELECT * FROM users`; // Prefer Prisma Client

// Don't ignore connection pooling in serverless
// Configure connection limit in DATABASE_URL
```

